<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause xmlns:xt="urn:xpressauthor:trackchanges" id="_da1678cb-ffc7-4e51-a6ec-f668d2208d8b" outputclass="ncc-clause"><meta><facet building="Class 1a"/><facet building="Class 1b"/><facet building="Class 2"/><facet building="Class 3"/><facet building="Class 4"/><facet building="Class 5"/><facet building="Class 6"/><facet building="Class 7a"/><facet building="Class 7b"/><facet building="Class 8"/><facet building="Class 9a"/><facet building="Class 9b"/><facet building="Class 9c"/><facet building="Class 10a"/><facet building="Class 10c"/></meta><sptc>J8D4</sptc><title id="_058783e7-5ddd-4a08-b7c4-0aff54f116f9">Swimming pool heating and pumping</title><archive-num/><subclause id="_3c798533-77b9-443f-95ad-d88c61c46f22" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_b17bc58b-d80b-455c-9eb0-44efc407a35d">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>Heating for a <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1487_0.7.0.xml#_4cbd9e00-0622-4dfd-9de4-913c80257732" id="_fcaea180-9698-4f0b-bd12-f64ae8678c4b" inv:access="external" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">swimming pool</xref> must be by—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_aca56172-39ad-4fa1-b38b-a17ef4a496b0">a solar heater; or</li><li id="_2a478144-38c2-474d-a225-79d5bf5037a5">a heater using reclaimed heat from another process such as reject heat from a refrigeration plant; or</li><li id="_a2920861-8e62-4f4d-9aaa-679778c7e567">a geothermal heater; or</li><li id="_6e703bb7-7320-419a-bb4b-c925ca52dd9f">a gas heater that achieves a minimum gross thermal efficiency of 90%; or</li><li id="_91a5184e-8c17-436f-bed1-cde6ee9aef4a">a heat pump; or</li><li id="_e06e8726-6157-4cb1-b443-3a7765c1ed6d">a combination of (a) to (e).</li></ol></subclause><subclause id="_de4ee1f5-ac38-4225-a5b7-4064da1fca07" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_af024bc8-3698-4deb-aebb-b07a1c793923">SubClause</title><num>2</num><p>Where some or all of the heating <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1432_4.0.0.xml#_af6fde9f-147d-4782-8b85-42044e80fd42" id="_5d6cb585-d2b0-4e97-a712-87d9d216a79d" inv:access="external" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">required</xref> by (1) is by a gas heater or a heat pump, the <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1487_0.7.0.xml#_4cbd9e00-0622-4dfd-9de4-913c80257732" id="_69fed310-4e8b-48aa-8cae-50debc899f5a" inv:access="external" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">swimming pool</xref> must have—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_6886a751-0e87-4970-83d9-3aacdf683afc">a cover with a minimum <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1420_0.4.0.xml#_e5acb40f-3d3d-4a3d-8987-f09f7eaadf77" id="_6d6f4232-d47d-494b-9e00-da2b90804516" inv:access="external" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">R-Value</xref> of 0.05; and</li><li id="_ca0f117a-2cc0-47c0-9244-472a91da1063">a time switch to control the operation of the heater.</li></ol></subclause><subclause id="_7c119f29-8bff-48dd-9b11-e9922f52a65f" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_0c8990cf-c716-4f33-857c-0c290ef82181">SubClause</title><num>3</num><p>A time switch must be provided to control the operation of a circulation pump for a <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1487_0.7.0.xml#_4cbd9e00-0622-4dfd-9de4-913c80257732" id="_ae350e0f-30cb-46c7-b958-7eeadc7f5d2e" inv:access="external" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">swimming pool</xref>.</p></subclause><subclause id="_0299337a-f04a-4ad1-9a0a-1dee9381e84a" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_0a68aab0-80d2-4a8e-aced-93f53362ae93">SubClause</title><num>4</num><p>Where <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1432_4.0.0.xml#_af6fde9f-147d-4782-8b85-42044e80fd42" id="_2d66a6f1-541c-4f14-acdb-b92b1e7f34c1" inv:access="external" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">required</xref>, a time switch must be capable of switching electric power on and off at variable pre-programmed times and on variable pre-programmed days.</p></subclause><subclause id="_2e5e4fc0-ee48-403f-8327-5a7576e5c277" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_9f8d48c0-c527-4970-b44a-47e1dba75cf7">SubClause</title><num>5</num><p>Pipework carrying heated or chilled water for a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1487_0.7.0.xml#_4cbd9e00-0622-4dfd-9de4-913c80257732" id="_d7354cf7-c250-4ae6-a159-92d394275db7" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">swimming pool</xref> must comply with the insulation requirements of <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/3442_4.14.0.xml#_50999247-ceaf-47bd-a08d-6422d3df8860" id="_40943120-2ad6-4ec1-b395-fa38442d458c" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="ncc-clause">J6D9</xref>.</p></subclause><subclause id="_c2c22844-89be-459b-bc78-f80387de11a5" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_ea5f7e34-03d9-45ec-a816-770900721745">SubClause</title><num>6</num><p>A building with gas heated water for a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1487_0.7.0.xml#_4cbd9e00-0622-4dfd-9de4-913c80257732" id="_3b4b5d07-f906-44ca-808a-c0444d7427f9" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">swimming pool</xref> must be provided with—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_de119785-f3bb-4e7d-81f5-5fdb20a36bb1">reserved electrical capacity sufficient to support future installation of air-source heat pump water heating equipment for the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1487_0.7.0.xml#_4cbd9e00-0622-4dfd-9de4-913c80257732" id="_fcfd4edc-afab-48e7-a424-37b2477e57ed" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">swimming pool</xref> assuming a nominal coefficient of performance of 3.25; and</li><li id="_a123a374-3ab8-4d4b-9e7d-7e4a89e3c8fd">reserved space within the main electrical distribution board comprising at least one empty three-phase circuit breaker slot and 4 DIN rail spaces per 35 kW of water heating capacity, labelled to indicate reservation for future installation of water heating equipment for the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1487_0.7.0.xml#_4cbd9e00-0622-4dfd-9de4-913c80257732" id="_15c906e3-a93f-43c6-8a8c-f8f58f81b163" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">swimming pool</xref>; and</li><li id="_2e4d564f-0151-47e3-8ad8-57a9b4694f1e">reserved space in the electrical riser or supply pathway for future <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1487_0.7.0.xml#_4cbd9e00-0622-4dfd-9de4-913c80257732" id="_ffe1e131-0421-45d5-913d-26362efc7480" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">swimming pool</xref> heating equipment sized in accordance with (a); and</li><li id="_a183230d-d81b-4b8c-bcb4-90e0821406be">reserved plant area with—<ol><li>space to accommodate heating plant of 7 m² plus 0.04 m²/kW of heating capacity; and</li><li>sufficient ventilation openings to achieve airflow of 115 L/s per kW of heating capacity with no recirculation of air; and</li></ol></li><li id="_a59253b2-c180-443d-bdfd-a32bd45346ca">a hot water circulation system that operates at a peak temperature of less than 50°C.</li></ol><subclause id="_8ba59679-c93c-4754-a003-f3a710892daa" outputclass="state-variation" variation="QLD" variation-type="REPLACE"><title id="_5241eca4-db34-41ec-ab76-13c28497c8cf">QLD REPLACE SubClause</title><num>6</num><p>This sub-clause has deliberately been left blank.</p></subclause></subclause><subclause id="_774944cd-8cd7-40ff-b01d-f4263d3d6624" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_d6fbff67-a7bb-4e91-8e07-593c2b86ecda">SubClause</title><num>7</num><p>The capacity and space <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1432_4.0.0.xml#_af6fde9f-147d-4782-8b85-42044e80fd42" id="_0c050cb5-a451-476b-b809-d4a27edbffbd" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">required</xref> by (6) must be sufficient to serve the same design load used to specify any gas-powered <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1487_0.7.0.xml#_4cbd9e00-0622-4dfd-9de4-913c80257732" id="_aa6b156f-1473-45da-b288-66f0918bd455" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">swimming pool</xref> water heating equipment.</p><subclause id="_f04c94cf-70e8-42fa-a591-92f3efabc136" outputclass="state-variation" variation="QLD" variation-type="REPLACE"><title id="_b9de4b6b-47b7-44b6-8a35-0a27d15934b3">QLD REPLACE SubClause</title><num>7</num><p>This sub-clause has deliberately been left blank.</p></subclause></subclause><subclause id="_5407ceb4-e2e8-4661-8caf-5fa7bdad295e" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_fc312cbc-948e-41cc-8e77-84a0dae60447">SubClause</title><num>8</num><p>For the purpose of J8D4, a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1487_0.7.0.xml#_4cbd9e00-0622-4dfd-9de4-913c80257732" id="_7befdcf0-7132-48c2-a608-035cf1180c9d" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">swimming pool</xref> does not include a spa pool.</p></subclause></clause>